  <summary>Distraction-free text editor for Markdown</summary>
  <description>
    <p>ghostwriter is a distraction-free text editor for Markdown featuring
       a live HTML preview as you type, theme creation, and document navigation
       in an aesthetic writing environment.  It comes with the Sundown Markdown
       processor built in, and can integrate with Pandoc, MultiMarkdown, and
       discount processors if they are installed.</p>
